                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check text-primary me-2"></i>Pengenalan Perusahaan</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check text-primary me-2"></i>Budaya Kerja & Nilai</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check text-primary me-2"></i>Prosedur Operasional</li>
